{"tid":2265512,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[填詞撚] 白羅斯民族曲 《白馬徽》(Pahonia) 粵語版本","createTime":"2020-10-31T13:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T01:50:08.000Z","uid":74151,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c837ac9a220ced67047f149b3d3130b6b4ec8d5f","tid":2265512,"uid":74151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"早前為咗聲援白羅斯10月25日全國大罷工，<br />\n我將佢哋嗰首民族歌曲/民間國歌 Pahonia，盡量跟原文歌詞原意寫成咗粵語版本<br />\n由於我唔識白羅斯文，我係睇住俄文維基嘅俄文翻譯嚟寫，可能會有少少出入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzYIQ8G7jQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFzYIQ8G7jQA&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=cd77f5ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzYIQ8G7jQA</a><br />\n粵語歌詞：<br />\n心中儆覺願垂記父兄愁難<br />\n毋忘故國烈夫踐血灘<br />\n銳閘堅比金湯抗萬方豪強<br />\n騎兵寶駿 令人戰惶惶<br />\n<br />\n皙木百轉 隙間飛過精駒<br />\n聲若震 意風發 千騎追<br />\n白馬徽高掛 戰甲不可低垂<br />\n未殺身 力竭聲靡萬敵難摧<br />\n<br />\n興衰千世 任年歲疾飛長河<br />\n前人老去 後生點繼火<br />\n大纛不倒 匆忽見浩海還田<br />\n旗桿所向 問誰領路前<br />\n<br />\n天佑世世子女不進魔手 <br />\n奸佞退散 兇惡驅走<br />\n叛棄家邦 勢必潦倒衰亡<br />\n難永當 莫教祖國落陷蠻荒<br />\n<br />\n堅心爭戰 用長劍盡斬仇頭<br />\n寧為炮屑 勿當他國狗<br />\n夜幕低掩 臆中痛裂久難眠<br />\n全因思國念民 憤義填<br />\n<br />\n珍重母國 生我長我家鄉<br />\n書頁罄斷古往家國殤<br />\n願報丕恩 我甘醉躺沙場<br />\n敵百槍 瀝血身殞六臟塗漿"},{"pid":"c943b8f3a714d7091d3ba7106261383cd82ea0a5","tid":2265512,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae937d8a3e10327f98023d51964a4f1595b7d47","tid":2265512,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"流明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5311abf4e26f73961d07d850ecec3ca384b791","tid":2265512,"uid":40641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"黐撚線，啲詞好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9830b2f35bea327cd1a42eb4f86d04e5ac4dbbe","tid":2265512,"uid":74784,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲詞後勁好強，文學修養超班<br />\n如果搵到多啲人唱和音啲氣勢真係震返白羅斯"},{"pid":"07215866dff034be272216e70dc53734b584066c","tid":2265512,"uid":364159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"Chur，強帖留名"},{"pid":"7255ea4e60b280615f1819625ff21ccb6c64ed59","tid":2265512,"uid":234457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"臨尾嗰兩段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0426bdde4d888ce19ad2f4f1c18ed99079051ce0","tid":2265512,"uid":234457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f58bcf662b1952d7109a6f7ef6ef5102c8265","tid":2265512,"uid":234457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"堅心爭戰 用長劍盡斬仇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d1e10a944d348fef6b954ecae7008cae7beb74","tid":2265512,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"聽聲轉基<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse